{"tid":1183512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[溫馨提示] 6.9 記得着black bloc","createTime":"2019-06-03T03:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T09:59:25.000Z","uid":30710,"like":287,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e43c3f9aa8276a61d85c81947b895b507de75c","tid":1183512,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請長期置頂<br />\n<br />\nReady bloc -全身黑色套裝 口罩<br />\n<br />\n//早於雨傘運動期間，「黑塊」戰術已有人提及，自去年年中，「本土民主前線」則多次在社交網站上提及這種戰術，並呼籲支持者身穿黑色T恤、深色長褲、戴口罩手套等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使示威者被捕，亦難於法庭上被舉證，又稱即使並非行動者，亦可以如此打扮，以掩護行動者。//<br />\n<br />\n早前初一審判亦有義士因為black bloc衣著，<br />\n無法證實係當事人而被判無罪<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">Credit to 香港獨立不是夢巴打<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NXZPivZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXZPivZ.png&h=35d7ef09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HsChspj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsChspj.png&h=5ce1160b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mni4RQ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMni4RQ0.png&h=5a38d3b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GR7EFKk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGR7EFKk.png&h=e0cd5f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KmWRwQ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKmWRwQ3.png&h=7db282d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">keep it up Hongkongese! </span>"},{"pid":"df72ce97b3da48720c8e2d9939a902e6b7ebd35c","tid":1183512,"uid":30710